      "value": "Chaffey Joint Union High is a High School Only district in San Bernardino County, serving about 22,116 students in 2024\u201325. About 3,239 students have an Individualized Education Program (IEP), and 446 of them \u2014 roughly 14% \u2014 have an autism (ASD) eligibility. Around 35% of those autistic students spend most of the school day, 80% or more, in a general-education classroom."
    },
